{"word":"μαλερός","slug":"μαλερός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>μαλερός</b></el> <el>(μᾰλερός, ή, όν) </el><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b><a href='S:μάλα'><el>μάλα</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>mighty, fierce, devouring, ravening</i>, of fire, <b><a href='S:Iliad'>Il.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a> <i>fiery, glowing, vehement, furious</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Tragic, in Tragic Greek'>Trag.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}